author: jonm
msg: HTTPCLIENT-975: added CacheConfig settings to provide more detailed
control over the background revalidation thread pool, and enabled
the stale-while-revalidate feature by default with a single worker
thread and a max queue size of 100 pending revalidations, which
should be a pretty safe setting.

author: philip
msg: Make 1.6-to-wcng upgrade handle replaced files that are not copied.
(write_entry): Non-copied working node always has its own op_depth.
(replaced_files): Expect and revert replacements that are not copied.
Update to include replacements that are not copies.
